06:40.068 --> 06:42.267
No, well, I just know how
hard you've been working

06:42.269 --> 06:44.970
on your diet, so I'm just trying
to be supportive. That's all.

06:44.972 --> 06:46.472
'Cause you know I
think you look amazing.

06:46.474 --> 06:48.307
- (CHUCKLES)
- Maybe.

06:48.309 --> 06:50.409
- CUSTOMER: Hey.
- (GROWLING)

06:50.411 --> 06:52.978
