07:11.599 --> 07:13.932
My dad loved Diamond, so, uh,

07:13.934 --> 07:16.101
it's embedded in my brain.

07:16.103 --> 07:18.036
Um...

07:18.038 --> 07:19.538
Yeah, man. If you just come on,

07:19.540 --> 07:21.775
I'll, uh, show you where to find it.

07:26.647 --> 07:30.015
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

07:30.017 --> 07:32.786
(MUTTERS)

07:35.623 --> 07:37.456
Oh, hey. Um, don't
forget your bathing suit,

07:37.458 --> 07:39.458
because, uh, this place
has, like, three pools.

07:39.460 --> 07:41.326
Great. (EXHALES)

07:41.328 --> 07:42.728
(SNIFFS)

07:42.730 --> 07:45.998
You know, I-I know it seems like a lot.

07:46.000 --> 07:47.666
But I've been chatting
with all the parents

07:47.668 --> 07:49.802
on the Facebook group,
and they seem really cool.

07:49.804 --> 07:51.637
And I think it's gonna
be good, you know,

07:51.639 --> 07:54.540
