08:46.945 --> 08:48.579
<i>on him last-minute, so...</i>

08:49.396 --> 08:51.598
Why don't I join you?

08:52.543 --> 08:53.665
Really?

08:53.667 --> 08:55.100
You want to come?

08:55.102 --> 08:56.301
I'm there.

08:56.303 --> 08:58.470
I've actually been wanting a...

08:58.472 --> 09:01.373
